high_descs: Walk straight towards the end of the room after crossing the couch and dining table. Stand before the cabinet.
Open the drawer and take the knife out of it.
Close the drawer and turn backwards and reach the oven which is next to the countertop.
Place the knife on the countertop in front of the oven.
Turn right and walk straight and once again stand in front of the cabinet.
Open the drawer and take the knife out of it and close the drawer.
Turn backwards and walk towards the countertop and reach it again.
Place the knife on the countertop in front of the oven next to the first knife.
anns.task_desc: Put the knives in front of the countertop.

high_descs: Cross the room to the cabinet past the couch, and fridge, go to the sink next to the microwave to your left.
Open the cabinet below the sink, pick up a knife from the sink, then close the cabinet
Go back to the countertop to your left.
Put the knife on the countertop in front of the microwave.
Go to the cabinet once again.
Open the cabinet below the sink, pick up another knife from the sink, then close the cabinet
Again go back to the countertop to your left.
Put the knife on the countertop besides the other knife in front of the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Pick up the knives from the sink, put them in front of the countertop

high_descs: Turn around and go to the cabinet area.
Open the knife cupboard below the sink.
Take the stick from the countertop.
Keep the knife near the countertop.
NOW GO TO THE SAME CABINET
Take another knife out from the cupboard.
Keep the stick near the microwave oven which is near the countertop.
Place the knife on the countertop.
anns.task_desc: Take two knives from cupboard and keep those in front of microwave oven.
